basic.Peptide Name: Defensin-like protein 1 (Defensin AMP1, CtAMP1; Plant defensin)
basic.Target Organism: Fungi:Botrytis cinerea (IC50=20 µg/ml), Cladosporium sphaerospermum (IC50=6 µg/ml), Fusarium culmorum (IC50=10 µg/ml), Leptosphaeria maculans (IC50=6 µg/ml), Penicillium digitatum (IC50=20 µg/ml), Trichoderma viride (IC50>100 µg/ml), Septoria tritiei (IC50=2 µg/ml), Verticilium albo-atrum (IC50=2 µg/ml), Neurospora crassa (IC50<0.3 µg/ml).
